name: COHMAP chron 2
notes: 3 C-14 dates in 194cm core. Bottom date 1355, but corrected for C-13 content. Bernabo (1977, Ph.D. thesis, Brown Univ.) Ragweed rise at 85cm. Date of 1700AD used for ragweed rise. Age bounds for application of the model: top = 0; bottom = 1000.
